To view from view, giving i32.
Let cells be buffer of 6 i32 filled with 0.
For each index i of cells: cells at i becomes i.
Let outer be view of cells from 1 for 4.
Let inner be view of outer from 1 for 2.
Let total be 0.
For each index i of inner: total becomes total plus inner at i.
Give total.

To main, giving i32.
Give view from view.
